---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Suivre ma commande — Micro Office"
description: "Suivez l'avancement de votre commande Micro Office avec votre référence et votre numéro de téléphone."
---

<section class="section-pad pb-10">
  <div class="container-content">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-xl">
      <p class="eyebrow">Suivi de commande</p>
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl font-bold leading-tight md:text-5xl">Où en est ma commande&nbsp;?</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-ink/70">Saisissez votre <span class="text-ink">référence</span> (ex. MO‑XXXX) et le <span class="text-ink">numéro de téléphone</span> utilisé lors de la commande.</p>

      <form id="track-form" class="mt-8 space-y-4">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div>
            <label for="t-ref" class="mb-2 block font-heading text-sm font-semibold">Référence *</label>
            <input id="t-ref" name="reference" type="text" required placeholder="MO-XXXX" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-ink/20 bg-white px-4 py-3 uppercase text-ink focus:border-red focus:outline-none">
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="t-tel" class="mb-2 block font-heading text-sm font-semibold">Téléphone *</label>
            <input id="t-tel" name="tel" type="tel" required placeholder="+223 …" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-ink/20 bg-white px-4 py-3 text-ink focus:border-red focus:outline-none">
          </div>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn-primary w-full sm:w-auto" data-track-submit>Suivre ma commande</button>
      </form>

      <p class="mt-4 hidden rounded-2xl border border-red/30 bg-red/5 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-red" data-track-error></p>

      {# Result #}
      <div class="mt-10 hidden" data-track-result>
        <div class="rounded-3xl border border-ink/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-soft">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2 border-b border-ink/10 pb-4">
            <span class="font-heading text-lg font-bold" data-track-ref></span>
            <span class="tag-mono text-ink/50" data-track-meta></span>
          </div>

          <ol class="mt-6 space-y-5" data-track-steps>
            {% set steps = ["reçue", "confirmée", "préparation", "expédiée", "livrée"] %}
            {% set labels = ["Reçue", "Confirmée", "En préparation", "Expédiée", "Livrée"] %}
            {% for s in steps %}
            <li class="flex items-center gap-4" data-step="{{ s }}">
              <span class="track-dot flex h-9 w-9 flex-none items-center justify-center rounded-full border-2 border-ink/15 text-ink/30">
                <svg class="h-4 w-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m5 12 5 5L20 7"/></svg>
              </span>
              <span class="font-heading text-sm font-semibold text-ink/50">{{ labels[loop.index0] }}</span>
            </li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ol>

          <div class="mt-6 hidden rounded-2xl bg-red/5 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-red" data-track-cancelled>Cette commande a été annulée. Contactez-nous pour plus d'informations.</div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-ink/50">Une question&nbsp;? <a href="https://wa.me/{{ site.whatsappNumber }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline hover:text-red">Écrivez-nous sur WhatsApp</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
